name: Stag
description:
Collaboration of paper, embroidery & illustration. All products are design & handmade in Melbourne. Our aim is to design clean, unique pieces of home décor.

Taupe Thread on 300gsm Watercolour Paper, 42 cm x 29.7cm

All orders will be shipped approximately 3 weeks after ordering As these are handmade items, we make everything to order- and we need time to make sure that your illustrations are noting but perfect! Payment must be made in full and have cleared before the item is shipped. If you are having any issues with PayPal, please do not hesitate to get in touch and I will assist you in anyway I can. 

Australian customers I will send your parcels via express post, which provides next day delivery to major centers. International shipping does take time (usually around 12-15 working days to the US) and I cannot guarantee a delivery time due to possible delays with customs. 
As all items are made to order, we will not accept returns for reasons other than damage- if an item is damaged, we will be happy to exchange the damaged goods for new ones. If for some reason we cannot fill your order, we will refund your payment. Please verify you paypal shipping address when placing your order- by purchasing from this site you are agreeing to take responsibility for these illustrations lost in the mail due to an incorrect address listed in the paypal transaction or held responsible for damage of items while in transit.

If you have any questions about any of my items or policies please do not hesitate to get in touch via projectsewn@hotmail.com or projectsewn on facebook All images and designs are subject to copyright and intellectual property conventions and practices. 
 
Thank you  
Projectsewn
